o\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where others would have seen the end, Murray refused to go down and accept the path that laid ahead of him.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"the path\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final defeat to Taylor Fritz and Tommy Paul was bruising, but it could have happened five days earlier.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Fritz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\"}, {\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.918645506586556e-20, \"text\": \"Tommy Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The final defeat\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Murray rewrote his last chapter.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his last chapter\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asthe curtain finally now falls, following defeat in the quarter-finals, there could not have been a more fitting way to mark it than at these Olympics.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asthe curtain\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"a more fitting way\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Murray was asked afterwards how he would like to he remembered, he replied: \\\"I think the last three matches have been a good example.\\\"\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last three matches\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"a good example\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or mark the final part of it, at least.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final part\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, the career of one of Britain's greatest ever athletes can be traced so closely through such distinct chapters; its defining moment arrived in ending Britain's 77-year wait for men'sWimbledonchampion.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2736, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8111098154502026, \"rank\": 0.23266353637639983, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8111098154502026, \"rank\": 0.23266353637639983, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the career\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"such distinct chapters\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"its defining moment\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that could not come without the heartbreak of painful defeats, nor the years of sheer graft that preceded them, chasing a dream that appeared out of reach.\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heartbreak\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"painful defeats\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"sheer graft\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cruel twist is the best part of Murray's career came to an end so abruptly, injuries denying him the chance to claim further titles that would have separated him from the rest of Britain's all-time greats.\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3111, \"end\": 3117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3258, \"end\": 3265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8111098154502026, \"rank\": 0.23266353637639983, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cruel twist\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"the best part\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"further titles\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he is a legend in a different class.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legend\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"a different class\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By all measures, Murray should have reached the end of his career five years ago, as the reality of his broken body threatened a premature end at the age 31.\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all measures\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"his broken body\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"a premature end\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the many remarkable aspects of Murray's journey is thatthe sporting obituaries have already been written, following that emotional press conference in Melbourne in 2019.\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3523, \"end\": 3529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3643, \"end\": 3652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9993548158347644, \"rank\": 0.0005480279536648338, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the many remarkable aspects\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"thatthe\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting obituaries\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"that emotional press conference\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They reflected a glorious story, one of resilience and heart to overcome the suffocating pressure at Wimbledon, and which spoke glowingly of the player and the person the lanky, guarded teenager from Dunblane grew up to be.\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunblane\", \"score\": 0.9999903870591902, \"rank\": 9.613031256722773e-06, \"text\": \"Dunblane\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunblane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunblane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a glorious story\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"the suffocating pressure\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3759}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"the player\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3813}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"the lanky, guarded teenager\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when that guard fell following his tears on Centre Court, he could be the most captivating force.\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3934, \"end\": 3946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that guard\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3905}, {\"ngram\": \"his tears\", \"from\": 3921, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"the most captivating force\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At his peak, Murray was as fierce a competitor as they come, a worthy challenger to the greatest players in the history of the sport in Roger Federer, Rafael Nadal and Novak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4002, \"end\": 4008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4125, \"end\": 4138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}, {\"begin\": 4140, \