", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray advocated for women's tennis and hired a female coach in Amelie Mauresmo, using his position to call for equality in the game.\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4347, \"end\": 4353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4411, \"end\": 4426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Am\\u00e9lie_Mauresmo\", \"score\": 0.9999999998108251, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amelie Mauresmo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Am\\u00e9lie_Mauresmo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Am\\u00e9lie_Mauresmo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women's tennis\", \"from\": 4368, \"to\": 4382}, {\"ngram\": \"a female coach\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"his position\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4446}, {\"ngram\": \"equality\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4467}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Murray battled back from hip resurfacing surgery, he extended the timeframe in which he could be an inspiration to others.\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4486, \"end\": 4492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hip resurfacing surgery\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4534}, {\"ngram\": \"the timeframe\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4561}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4597}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he was unable to get back to competing for the biggest titles since returning, everything that followed was a bonus and a gift, right through to these Olympics.\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest titles\", \"from\": 4658, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4704}, {\"ngram\": \"a bonus\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4730}, {\"ngram\": \"a gift\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray's legacy may be defined by his historic Wimbledon title, but it will not just be measured in wins or defeats.\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4777, \"end\": 4783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his historic Wimbledon title\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4839}, {\"ngram\": \"wins\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4881}, {\"ngram\": \"defeats\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 4892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In sport, moments of true triumph can be fleeting.\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 4897, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 4911}, {\"ngram\": \"true triumph\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even for those like Murray whose achievements are immortalised within history, the majority of athletes spend their career chasing the esteem that he became to be held in.\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 5116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4965, \"end\": 4971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whose achievements\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 4990}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5022}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5036}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5040, \"to\": 5048}, {\"ngram\": \"their career\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"the esteem\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not that Murray went looking for it, instead remaining true to the values of hard work and decency that made him such a relatable champion as he fought to the very end.\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5126, \"end\": 5132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067881527086622e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5203}, {\"ngram\": \"decency\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5215}, {\"ngram\": \"the very end\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even as his body let him down, the heart remained.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5302}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like searching for that final Olympic pin to add to his collection, he remained himself until the last: a monumental figure in British sporting history, the likes of which may never be seen again.\", \"from\": 5337, \"t